import React,{ Component } from "react" import axios from "axios" const SignupPage = ()=> { const postReq = (e)=>{ console.log("Name: ", e.target.name) console.log("Email: ", e.target.email) console.log("Password: ", e.target.password) axios.post("/user/insert",{ data:{ name: e.target.name, email: e.target.email, password: e.target.password } }) e.preventDefault() } return (
SIGN UP
); } export default SignupPage;
